Project paused (I won't update it for now)

# VERY IMPORTANT
- ! DO NOT USES THIS MOD WITH OTHER PEOPLE OR ON SERVER SIDE, ONLY USE IT IN A SOLO WORLD, CLIENT SIDE ! (Multiplayer coming soon)
- ! INCOMPATIBLE WITH OTHER MODS, TRY AT YOUR OWN RISKS !
- ! REI / JEI and others mods like these are recommended for the crafts !
- I'm thinking to do a fabric version

# What does this mod add to the game ? 📖
This mod add a lot of basic features:

## New ores
- Alderium, used principally to make tools, armors and a backpack, a little better than netherite;
- Endersteel, same uses that Alderium, a little better than it;
- Neantite, same uses that Endersteel + a multitool, a little better than it;
- Blue Topaz, same uses that the precedents ores, same stats as iron, when you have the helmet on you, it gives you water breathing;
- A full obsidian armor and tools set, tools have the same stats as iron, better toughness than netherite, better knockback resistance than netherite and best enchantability in the game.
- Alminium, used to create a new flint and steel (Netherite and steel) to access to a new dimension.

## Miscellaneous things
- A pocket (a little backpack);
- A home system with an interface (up to 5 homes) :
-![Homes GUI](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/215d1c83231641b8331182d22738c2e128d801a1.png)
- Fuze Tea;
- An Admin interface where you have access to some admin features that are in the game :
- ![Admin Tools GUI](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e94f8fc5f41e4750ffc1e66e2af6f7ca74216a73.png)
- An interface where you can access to the "Homes" interface, the "Admin Tools" interface, the "Other Tools" interface and the "Solar System" interface :
- ![List GUI](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d8d116810477a2ea44bf464976800c9173f5ea48.png)
- A cartoon bow with an aimbot;
- A Air sword which gives you some effects :
- ![Air sword effects](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/dae05e28d918dcdd7ecf6183387faaafed191b9d.png) When you are sneaking, the slow falling effect is removed;
- A God sword which summon a thunderbolt when you hit an entity;
- Paintings;
- Food (biscuit, banana);
- When you are on fire, it says how many time you will be on fire :
- ![Fire time](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/08da95736d84370556a9e7c3175241868fb8fb80.png)
- If you are in a solid wall, you are teleported to the surface;
- A Solar System interface where you can tp on other planets (only at 10+ experience levels), and on the sun (only at 100+ experience levels) :
- ![Solar System GUI](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7d64a5e95e66e2d49b6507dd3dec503c54f22d8c.png)
- A piece of clothing, obtainable when fishing. This is used to create clothes with the same stats than a leather armor;
- An amethyst jewel that don't burn and can be used to create "The Stick", which is an OP stick;
- There are also some other little features but I let you discover them !

# Commands
- /!fly (you must be flying to disable the fly with the command);
- /!fire (set you on fire for x seconds);
- /!extinguish (stop you from being in fire);
- /!god (disable all damages and make hostile mobs ignore you);
- /!ungod (enable all damages and make hostile mobs not ignore you anymore);
- /!sethome (save the dimension and the coordinates where you are) you can set only 1 home;
- /!home (go to the saved dimension and coordinates);

# Languages

For the moment, all things that this mod add is in english. I plan to add French later.
I know there are some issues in my english, I'll correct them later

